T1  - Serum complexed and free prostate-specific antigen (PSA) for the diagnosis of the polycystic ovarian syndrome (PCOS)
A1  - Diamandis E.P.
A1  - Stanczyk F.Z.
A1  - Wheeler S.
A1  - Mathew A.
A1  - Stengelin M.
A1  - Nikolenko G.
